locality: Along Route National 7, at Isalo; low shrubby vegetation at the base of rock outcrop.
District de Beroroha, commune d'Antanamary, fokontany d'Antanamary, Rivière Mahasoa (Makay). Collectés avec Zafimahefa Brunot et Mahereza.
Isalo National Park. Tapia forest of Ankejabe, 2-3 km N of National Route #7. Collected with F. Rakotonasolo. Specimens preserved in alcohol.

Ilakaka, near the Isalo Mountains, a few km SW of village of Ilakaka, S of RN 7, extensive savanna o Bismarckia nobilis (blue form), rocky outcrops of limestone and sedimentary rocks, grass and other herbaceous ground plants.
Above the Grotte (Grotto) along the Grotto Circuit at Cap St. Marie Special Reserve
